{"id":294394,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/【麻辣总局】柴静对话张艺谋/","date":"2013-05-20T23:05:29Z","modified":"2013-05-20T23:17:05Z","title":"【麻辣总局】柴静对话张艺谋","content":"<p>最近大导演张艺谋陷入“孩儿门”，有知情人爆料说张导有7个葫芦娃。国人好八卦，围观者众。为解众国人之疑惑，央视著名记者柴静在神网友的安排下，在第一时间采访了张大导演。面对柴静犀利刁钻的提问，张导面带微笑，坦然作答。下面是采访画面截图<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://blog.sciencenet.cn/static/ueditor/dialogs/emotion/images/jx2/j_0059.gif\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/zhangyimou.jpg\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/zhangyimou.jpg\" alt=\"zhangyimou\" width=\"416\" height=\"4078\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-294398\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.google.com/url?sa=t&#038;rct=j&#038;q=柴静对话张艺谋&#038;source=web&#038;cd=30&#038;ved=0CHoQFjAJOBQ&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sciencenet.cn%2Fblog-40615-691357.html&#038;ei=ta6aUZyaK-qqiAKjpIHACQ&#038;usg=AFQjCNH4oRTwpIjBEEoKD5tTpk0rTIGuqg&#038;sig2=3A4uKlMdyMoCCuGEn0HLLQ&#038;bvm=bv.46751780,bs.1,d.cGE\">原文链接</a>： 科学网。</p>\n","author":296,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203,13789],"tags":[5908,171,10853,8984,20837]}